codes.code: argmax 'Complete the sentence by filling in the ~. If there are multiple ~s, use your knowledge of the Latin language to fill in the missing ~ characters. Provide the answer only. Quī ab amīcīs proficīsc~ laet~ nōn potest. Choose from this set of possible answers [ entur iuntur, untur, itur, itur ētur untur itur, ī ārī, itur ārī] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'entur iuntur', 'untur', 'itur', 'itur ētur untur itur', 'ī ārī', 'itur ārī']
